---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Get Factory Pricing - Sunlit Solar Roof" description="Start a factory pricing conversation for solar roof tiles, metal solar roof sheets, inactive roof elements and accessories. Drawings help but are not required for the first message.">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      <p class="sunlit-overline mb-4">Start with what you have</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Get Factory Pricing or Ask a Product Question</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        A roof drawing helps, but it is not required for the first conversation. Send your country, estimated roof area, project type, photos, product interest or any basic question. We will help you choose the right next step.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">China Manufacturer Contact</h2>
            <p class="mb-2"><a href="mailto:info@sunlitsolarroof.com" class="text-green-700 font-semibold">info@sunlitsolarroof.com</a></p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Changzhou, Jiangsu, China</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-soft-green border border-border p-5 text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed">
            <p class="font-heading font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">What we can discuss</p>
            <p>Product fit, rough budget, active and inactive roof elements, matching accessories, samples, packing, shipping terms and project-based quotation direction. Local roofing and electrical work should be handled by qualified local professionals.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border p-5 text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed">
            <p class="font-heading font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Useful information, not mandatory</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>• Project country or delivery destination</li>
              <li>• Estimated roof area or building type</li>
              <li>• Preferred product line: Lumina Slate or Storm Guard</li>
              <li>• Photos, sketches or roof drawings if available</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <form class="space-y-4 sunlit-card p-6" method="POST" action="/thank-you/">
          <input name="name" required placeholder="Full Name" class="w-full border rounded-lg px-4 py-3" />
          <input name="email" type="email" required placeholder="Email" class="w-full border rounded-lg px-4 py-3" />
          <input name="company" placeholder="Company / Organization (optional)" class="w-full border rounded-lg px-4 py-3" />
          <input name="country" placeholder="Project Country / Delivery Region (optional)" class="w-full border rounded-lg px-4 py-3" />
          <select name="buyerType" class="w-full border rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
            <option value="">Buyer Type (optional)</option>
            <option value="distributor">Distributor / Importer</option>
            <option value="installer">Solar Installer</option>
            <option value="contractor">Roofing Contractor</option>
            <option value="developer">Developer</option>
            <option value="homeowner">Project Owner / Homeowner</option>
            <option value="other">Other</option>
          </select>
          <select name="productInterest" class="w-full border rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
            <option value="">Product Interest (optional)</option>
            <option value="lumina-slate">Lumina Slate Glass Solar Roof Tiles</option>
            <option value="storm-guard">Storm Guard Metal Solar Roof Sheets</option>
            <option value="not-sure">Not sure yet</option>
          </select>
          <textarea name="message" required placeholder="Tell us what you know today: rough roof area, project type, target country, question, or drawing/photo link if available" class="w-full border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 h-36"></textarea>
          <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-green-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg">Start Factory Pricing Conversation</button>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate text-center">No full drawing required for the first message.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
